==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Clouding
<hw>Cloud"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A mottled appearance
given to ribbons and silks in the process of dyeing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A diversity of colors in yarn, recurring at regular
intervals.</def> <rj><au>Knight.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cloudland</ent>⟦br⟧
